\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Akademie vir Reformatoriese Opleiding en Studies \'28AROS\'29 is not registered with the Department of Education as a private higher education provider. The institution does not yet have any programmes accredited by the HEQC.\line \line An application for a similar programme was tabled at the Accreditation Committee meeting of 26 May 2010 and it was not accredited. This is a new application to offer a BEd in the Foundation Phase.\line \cell \pard 

